videos.title: Baby Siege Rhino, New Mox and Spirits Dragons  Tarkir Dragonstorm MTG Spoilers
videos.description:
We got an early look at Khans: Dragonstorm today and the set looks amazing! There's a baby Siege Rhino, a new Mox, a bunch of cool callbacks to original Khans of Tarkir and, of course, a ton of Dragon stuff!

Today's video is brought to you by Card Kingdom. You can pick up some Magic: the Gathering cards (and help support the show) at https://www.carkdingdom.com/mtggoldfish

More spoilers: https://www.mtgpreviews.com
